</pdfaProperty:description>
                           <pdfaProperty:name>issn</pdfaProperty:name>
                           <pdfaProperty:valueType>Text</pdfaProperty:valueType>
                        </rdf:li>
                        <rdf:li rdf:parseType="Resource">
                           <pdfaProperty:category>external</pdfaProperty:category>
                           <pdfaProperty:description>Title of the magazine, or other publication, in which a resource was/will be published. 
Typically this will be used to provide the name of the magazine an article appeared in as metadata for the article, along with information such as the article title, the publisher, volume, number, and cover date. 

Note: Publication name can be used to differentiate between a print magazine and the online version if the names are different such as ‚Äúmagazine‚ÄĚ and ‚Äúmagazine.com.‚ÄĚ 
</pdfaProperty:description>
                           <pdfaProperty:name>publicationName</pdfaProperty:name>
